Module chromatynk.chromatynk_g6
Package chromatynk.chromatynk_g6.diagnostic

Record Class LYnkIssue

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
chromatynk.chromatynk_g6.diagnostic.LYnkIssue
Record Components:
type - Either ERROR or WARNING depending on the issue context (Use IssueType)
message - The message to emit.
lineNumber - The line number in the input where the issue occurred.
lineOffset - The character position within that line where the issue occurred.
details - Additional comments for debugging the code.
public record LYnkIssue(IssueType type, String message, int lineNumber, int lineOffset, String details) extends Record
Base Object that represents an issue that occurred in an input. Used for UI and Debug purposes.
